No. D-2859. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 7, 2015.

In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF William Jennings JEFFERSON.

Williams Jennings Jefferson, of New Orleans, Louisiana, is suspended from the *612practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
